snippet.title: Arcade Longplay - Star Fire (1979) by Exidy
snippet.description: Full playthrough of the game Star Fire for Arcade machines. Released back in 1979 by Exidy, the game is very nice and colorful space shooter with resemblance to the movie Star Wars.
